The paper deals with the problem of computing the probability of a sum of random variables, which is a fundamental problem in probability theory and statistics. This problem is closely related to several areas of computer science, including data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), and probability (cs.PR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
